### Get session config
# Returns everything the FE needs to render the "create session" form:
# place types, sort options, and radius constraints (in miles).
# Called once when the create-session page loads.

GET https://{{choosee-api-host}}/v1/sessions/config HTTP/1.1

# Response 200:
# {
